"{\"uid\": \"metro.co.uk-2024-08-09-viral-turkish-olympic-shooter-explains-truth-behind-iconic-pose-21396354\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Yusuf Dikec, theOlympicshooter who has become a viral sensation at theParisGames, has lifted the lid on his iconic pose.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 120, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 0, \"end\": 5, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cat_Stevens\", \"score\": 0.7194127755515969, \"rank\": 0.3897675720948555, \"text\": \"Yusuf\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cat_Stevens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cat_Stevens\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dikec produced an impressive display in the 10-metre air pistol to claim silver alongside teammate Sevval Ilayda Tarhan.\", \"from\": 122, \"to\": 242, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But it was the 51-year-old's extremely laid-back pose and lack of high-tech eye equipmentthat caught the eye of viewers.\", \"from\": 244, \"to\": 364, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Having gone viral onsocial media, the shooter has seen other athletes, including Swedish pole vaulter Armand Duplantis, celebrate using his now iconic pose.\", \"from\": 366, \"to\": 522, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 447, \"end\": 454, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\", \"score\": 0.9999944082077854, \"rank\": 3.230867855727807e-06, \"text\": \"Swedish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sweden\"}, {\"begin\": 468, \"end\": 484, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armand_Duplantis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Armand Duplantis\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armand_Duplantis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Armand_Duplantis\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Dikec, competing in his fifth Games, has now revealed that his calm demeanour did 